      title: Approve a policy change
      intent: Authorized actors approve or reject policy versions.
      touches_entities:
        - Policy
        - Policy Version
        - Approval Decision
    - use_case_id: UC-SYS-002
      title: Record a governed execution
      intent: The platform records governed execution outcomes and evidence.
      touches_entities:
        - Execution Record
        - Evidence Record
    - use_case_id: UC-SYS-003
      title: Manage retention and deletion
      intent: Operators define retention policy and track deletions.
      touches_entities:
        - Retention Rule
        - Deletion Request
